  "texts": [
    "We iteratively expanded the system prompt based on the LLM's performance and errors observed during runs on the development set.",
    "All iterations and performance metrics are reported in the Results section, and were performed with GPT-4 alone, as it proved to be the most efficient system.",
    "The code for generating the various prompts is available in the KEEPER R package.",
    "(https://github.com/OHDSI/Keeper/tree/v0.2.0).",
    "The responses of the LLMs are parsed using a simple approach, removing all but the 'Summary' section and looking for keywords such as 'yes' and 'no'."
  ],
